GeneralComments:
24/7
Two reserved car parks and two charging stations. The first is an ABB fast charger with three tethered cables: CHAdeMO, CCS Combo (Type 1), and a Type 2 (43kW) AC. Adjacent to this is a second charging station with two Type 2 (22kW) socket outlets (which will require EV drivers to supply their own cable). The chargers operate 24/7 however a Charge.net.nz RFID is required for their use. There's WIFI across the road from the local library.
